      "date": "2013-05-08 04:47:01.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on el6/x86_64, unknown/unknown: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/4f9983d0-b79a-11e2-b384-52540035b04c).  Ran 1 tests.  1 tests failed: node-provisioning-1.",
